Class AppliedRule

java.lang.Object
  edu.rpi.phil.legup.AppliedRule
public class AppliedRule
extends java.lang.Object

A rule that was applied as the transition between two states. An AppliedRule is also an edge in the Puzzle Tree.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Drew Housten
